  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8a\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd -\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b9a\u0bbf.\u0b9a\u0bbf.\u0b9f\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Attack on journalists near Prime Minister's residence - CCD initiates investigations",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Amidst the protests that started demanding the resignation of the President and the Prime Minister, Sirasa, Shakthi R.V., who went for media activities. The Colombo Crime Prevention Unit has started investigations into the incident in which four journalists were assaulted in front of Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe's house.",
        "In this regard, the officers of the Colombo Crime Prevention Unit presented the matter through a report to Colombo Additional Magistrate Harshana Kegunawala today (12) and received orders for investigations.",
        "Accordingly, Justice Harshana Kekunawala ordered all the media to provide the unedited videos related to the attack to the investigators.",
        "On the night of the 9th, video cameraman of Sirasa TV Varuna Sampath, office reporter Sarasi Peiris, internet journalist Jannitha Mendis Shakthi R.V. went to collect information about the tension near the Prime Minister's residence. Journalist Sindhujan and others were assaulted by the police on duty there.",
        "While this incident has caused a great shock, it is also noteworthy that Romesh Lienake, who is said to have acted as the commanding officer of the Police Special Action Force who participated in the attack, has been temporarily suspended."
      ],
